---
---
<section class="py-40 px-8 bg-surface-container-low" data-section="process">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-24 gap-8">
      <h3 class="font-headline text-6xl font-bold leading-tight" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">O caminho <br />da clareza.</h3>
      <p class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-outline pb-2" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade">Etapas do projeto</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-white/5" data-stagger>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] ease-[var(--ease-out)]" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-light text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] block mb-12">01</span>
        <h5 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Entendimento</h5>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Mergulho profundo nos desafios e objetivos reais do seu negócio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] ease-[var(--ease-out)]" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-light text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] block mb-12">02</span>
        <h5 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Direção</h5>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Definição da arquitetura e das ferramentas ideais para o seu contexto.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] ease-[var(--ease-out)]" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-light text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] block mb-12">03</span>
        <h5 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Construção</h5>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Desenvolvimento ágil com foco total em usabilidade e performance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] ease-[var(--ease-out)]" data-animate="reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-light text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-base)] block mb-12">04</span>
        <h5 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Entrega</h5>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Acompanhamento no lançamento e suporte contínuo para evolução.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
